highlights.text: “I Remember Everything (feat. Kacey Musgraves)” by Zach Bryan and Kacey Musgraves is the highest new entry on Top Songs USA at #1.
Zach Bryan has the most spots on Top Songs USA. “I Remember Everything (feat. Kacey Musgraves)” is the highest at #1.
“Burn, Burn, Burn” by Zach Bryan is the biggest gainer on Top Songs USA, up 36 spots at #108.
“No Role Modelz” by J. Cole has been on Top Songs USA the longest, at 171 weeks straight.
